race.description: Tabtouch Have You Got The Touch Maiden
race.comment: QUESTIONEVERYTHING (1) showed enough on debut when jumping the race favourite, just bumping into one who was much better on the day. The stable's strike jockey hops aboard now and he has the speed to roll across from the draw. Can land the knockout blow this time around. AMERICAN QUE TEE (5) just missed here 13 days ago over the short course and steps up in distance. The way she finished off suggested the rise in trip is a big tick and Whiting remains in the saddle. Fitter now and can make her presence felt. MYSTIC CHAOS (10) finished 1L off the winner here last time out, hitting the line alongside AMERICAN QUE TEE. This looks a much better scenario for her today with a better draw and a rise in trip. LARAKINISM (2) was $151 first-up at Northam but was off a very long break there. Easier here and improvement is likely. NO COMEBACKS (9) should appreciate this trip first-up and is not out of this on debut.
